channel.title: Does 14 day member trials account have a limit?
channel.description:
i decided to make another thread, because the other was not really "understandable" xD
soo... my question is: does 14day runescape membership trials account has a limit, because i tried to make 1 yesterday and it was f2p :S

item.title: Does 14 day member trials account have a limit?

[quote=“mr extremez, post:5, topic:441043”][quote author=FusionX link=topic=543721.msg3985391#msg3985391 date=1335820403]
i know, but i mean, is there a limit on the account i could make :S how much account i can make with 14 days memb
[/quote]Theres no limit but what’s the point of making more and more accounts?.. You lose your progress every time. And with the trials you can only bank 300 of an item. And sell 50 of an item at a time at the ge.[/quote]

why i can’t create 1 ? :S
